{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"Overview"},{"type":"heading","text":"Badge","level":3,"anchor":"Badge"},{"type":"tabNavigator","tabs":[{"title":"Orange","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_badge_Orange"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"title":"Orange Compact","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_badge_OrangeCompact"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"title":"Sosh","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_badge_Sosh"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"title":"Wireframe","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_badge_Wireframe"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBadge","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is a small UI element used to highlight status, notifications, or categorization within an interface. It is often displayed as a label or indicator with a distinct background color and text."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Info badge in medium size without information","OUDSBadge(status: .info, size: .medium)","","\/\/ Negative badge in medium size with count information","OUDSBadge(count: 1, status: .negative, size: .medium)","","\/\/ Neutral badge in medium size with an image","OUDSBadge(status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\")), accessibilityLabel: \"Like\", size: .medium)"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Tag","level":3,"anchor":"Tag"},{"type":"tabNavigator","tabs":[{"title":"Orange","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_Orange"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"title":"Orange Compact","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_OrangeCompact"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"title":"Sosh","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_Sosh"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"title":"Wireframe","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_Wireframe"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is a small element that shows short information like a label, keyword, or category. It helps users quickly find, group, or understand content."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Text only with neutral status, for emphasized appearance with rounded shape in default size","OUDSTag(label: \"Label\",  status: .neutral(), appearance: .emphasized, shape: .rounded, size: .default)","\/\/ Or also","OUDSTag(label: \"Label\")","            ","\/\/ Tag with negative status with bullet","OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .negative(leading: .bullet)","            ","\/\/ Tag with neutral status with a custom decorative icon","OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\")))","\/\/ If your layout is in RTL mode but your tag has an icon with another meaning because of bad orientation,","\/\/ you can flip the icon","OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"), flipIcon: true))","            ","\/\/ Text with neutral status with bullet","OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(bullet: true))","            ","\/\/ Tag with loader with rounded shape in small size","OUDSTag(loadingLabel: \"Label\", shape: .rounded, size: .small)"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Input Tag","level":3,"anchor":"Input-Tag"},{"type":"tabNavigator","tabs":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_inputTag_Orange","type":"image"}]}],"title":"Orange"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_inputTag_OrangeCompact","type":"image"}]}],"title":"Orange Compact"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_inputTag_Sosh","type":"image"}]}],"title":"Sosh"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_inputTag_Wireframe","type":"image"}]}],"title":"Wireframe"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSInputTag","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" is a small element that shows short information like a label, keyword, or category, which can be removed or changed on tap.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Create an input tag","OUDSInputTag(\"Label\") {","    \/\/ Do something, usually remove itself from a list","}","    ","\/\/ Show in a list and remove when clicked","var names: [String] = [ \"Foo\", \"Bar\", \"Wizz\" ]","    ","ForEach(names, id: \\.self) { name in","    OUDSInputTag(label: name) {","        if let index = names.firstIndex(of: name) {","            names.remove(at: index)","        }","    }","}"]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Indicators","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Some components can be used for "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"indicators"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/indicators"]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"role":"article","title":"Indicators","roleHeading":"Article","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"images":[{"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png","type":"icon"},{"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png","type":"card"}]},"references":{"component_inputTag_Sosh":{"alt":"An input tag component in light and dark modes with Sosh theme","type":"image","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"ur